---
title: Warm Farro & Shrimp Bowl with Wax Beans, Sweet Bell Pepper & Shallot Citronette
description: Farro is an ideal base for any grain bowl—it’s not only nutritious, but nutty and delightfully chewy to boot! Tossed together with juicy shrimp, crispy-tender wax beans, and caramelized bell pepper, this salad is one of our all-time favorites. Lemony shallot citronette is a great staple dressing to keep in your back pocket!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5570a0e9f8b25ee8798b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/5570a0e9f8b25ee8798b4568.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/warm-farro-and-shrimp-bowl-5570a0e9f8b25ee8798b4568
time required: 40 minutes
cuisine: North America
